      "text": "I have zero clue how people get all these drone shots. I literally went for 19 days and wasnt allowed to fly my drone anywhere. Osaka, Kyoto, Kinosaki, Mt. Fuji or Tokyo. Im jealous. They either got permission from the government or I dont know what. I even registered the drone with Japan and everywhere I went I was told it was illegal. That shot near the temple in Kyoto is insane.",
